the balloon pump looks like a cylinder with four legs similar to the crafting table, it has an input and an output, a platform on the top and a tube on the side

i made this suggestion because some maps have little to no balloons (looking at you shroomy land) and this would be a good way to get them, while hopefully not being too cheap and overpowered that you could craft a bunch of big balloons and air tanks

Flag
suggestion.description:
The flag is crafted with 1 truss and 2 fabric
Upon being crafted, the flag will display the avatar of its original crafter on it. 
The flag acts as a form of item control: anything that is connected to the flag with rope can only be tampered with by the owner of the flag, allowing for what is essentially claiming of items, though limited to a small range. In team elimination games, the flag will be replaced by a generic team color, and all team members are allowed to use claimed blocks. 

This part is intended to provide security for boat builders, however there is one way to counter it: when a laser is fired at the flag, it will immediately burn up and all previously claimed blocks will be unclaimed. This is to prevent people from abusing the flag in pvp modes, and keeps griefing enemy boats as a valid method of combat.
